<%= email_eyebrow "Almost there" %>

<h1 style="font-family: 'Newsreader', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 23px; line-height: 1.18; margin: 0 0 12px; color: #171008;">
  Confirm your email, @<%= @user.handle %>.
</h1>

<p style="margin: 0 0 18px;">
  One click and your XbutforY account is live — you&rsquo;ll be able to submit
  sites, vote on the ones that earn it, and get the Sunday digest. It keeps the
  index human.
</p>

<%= email_button "Confirm my email", confirm_email_url(token: @token) %>

<p style="margin: 16px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: #6b5d4a;">
  The link is good for two days. Didn&rsquo;t create this account? Ignore this
  email and nothing happens.
</p>
